column40:
Overall, the environment seems to be well maintained. There is very little litter on the ground, and there is a lot of waste disposal cans available throughout the green space areas.
There was very little vandalism, with the only instances being on the playground's walls.

 Since it is day time I could not evaluate the street lamps' functionality, though they were clean and there were no signs of deterioration. The benches are clean, garbage cans and signs were visible and in good shape.

The green space is well maintained and cared after, with evidence of recent lawn maintenance and plant watering. Floral arrangements and gardens are present in the area and are well maintained.
